Consolidated Grandview Inc said itacquired a 60 pct stake in &lt;All Ticket Group PLC>, of London,for undisclosed terms. The seller was also undisclosed.    All Ticket is a special events travel company withexclusive European rights to UAL Inc &lt;UAL>'s United AirlinesApollo system, booking all United Airlines flights in Britainand Europe. All Ticket and its subsidiaries will alsoco-sponsor various events this year including the British Opengolf tournament and rowing's Henley Regatta.    Its 1986 revenues totaled 12 mln Canadian dlrs.    Reuter&#3;